SUMMARY:Lancaster Symphony Orchestra - FREE Open Rehearsal
DESCRIPTION:Open Rehearsals offer community members of all ages a free and unique opportunity to view a working symphonic rehearsal. As the musicians work on particular passages\, attendees get a behind-the-scenes look at how a performance moves from a work in progress to a work of art. LSO Open Rehearsals are free\, have general seating\, and are available on a first-come\, first-served basis. The Gardner Theater is ADA Compliant and easily accessible for wheelchairs\, walkers\, and strollers
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/lancaster-symphony-orchestra-free-open-rehearsal/
LOCATION:Gardner Theatre within Lancaster Country Day School\, 725 Hamilton Road\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Music and Dance
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/December-2023-2-2.jpg
END:VEVENT
