SUMMARY:Friday Night Improv: ☆ Luxury Gas ☆
DESCRIPTION:Witness the stylings of Lancaster Improv Players’ newest house team; an evening of delightful discoveries for players and audience alike! Our newest house team makes their way to the stage with a LIP-grown show style known as ‘Parfait’. Where does the long form end and the short form begin? Come find out for yourself! BYOB $15 at the door Due to the size of our theater\, there is a quick turnover time between our scheduled shows. If you purchase tickets to both events on Friday evening\, you will be asked to wait outside during the break so that the next team can warm up before the audience returns. LANCASTER IMPROV PLAYERS is an intimate black box venue located in the heart of Lancaster City. With a capacity of approximately 30 guests\, that means this Lancaster comedy club is entirely front row. Not a nosebleed in sight! After all\, BYOB is just a drink special you never get tired of.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/friday-night-improv-%e2%98%86-luxury-gas-%e2%98%86-2/
LOCATION:The Lancaster Improv Theater\, 16 S Prince Str\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
