SUMMARY:Brewery Tours: Lancaster City Walk-a-Bout
DESCRIPTION:Discover Lancaster City One Sip at a Time! \n\n\n\nStep into the heart of craft beer country with Brewery Tours’ Lancaster City Walk-a-Bout! \n\n\n\nJoin our fun and knowledgeable Beer Guides as we stroll through beautiful downtown Lancaster City\, visiting three of the city’s best craft breweries along the way. Guests will enjoy guided tastings of twelve incredible local beers while hearing behind-the-scenes brewery stories and discovering the history\, culture\, and character that makes Lancaster’s craft beer scene so special. \n\n\n\nWhat to Expect: \n\n\n\n– Visit three Lancaster City craft breweries \n\n\n\n– Guided tastings of a curated selection of locally brewed beers \n\n\n\n– Entertaining beer history and brewery insights \n\n\n\n– A relaxed walking experience through vibrant downtown Lancaster \n\n\n\nWhether you’re a craft beer enthusiast or just looking for a fun way to explore the city\, the Lancaster City Walk-a-Bout is the perfect blend of beer\, history\, and adventure. \n\n\n\nGrab your friends\, lace up your walking shoes\, and let’s explore Lancaster—one great beer at a time. \n\n\n\nBook your spot today with Brewery Tours! \n\n\n\nThis craft beer experience runs most Saturdays throughout the year. Advanced booking is required at www.UltimateCraftBeerExperience.com.  \n\n\n\nThis is a 21+ experience only.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/brewery-tours-lancaster-city-walk-a-bout/
LOCATION:PA
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/cityoflancasterpa-242134369851055-6489455863566075195-Discover-Lancaster-12-1.png
END:VEVENT
