SUMMARY:Saturday Night Improv: Pandamonium
DESCRIPTION:An Improv Showdown for the heart of Lancaster City! PANDAMONIUM\, an IMPROV SHOWDOWN\, is coached by Mike Andrews\, LIP’s short form improv assassin. If you like shows like Make Some Noise or Whose Line Is It Anyway\, then you already have a taste for short form improv games\, which is what Pandamonium is primed to provide. Vote on your favorite scenes and see how the competition shakes out! BYOB $15 at the door Due to the size of our theater\, there is a quick turnover time between our scheduled shows. If you purchase tickets to both events on Saturday evening\, you will be asked to wait outside during the break so that the next team can warm up before the audience returns. LANCASTER IMPROV PLAYERS is an intimate black box venue located in the heart of Lancaster City. With a capacity of approximately 30 guests\, that means this Lancaster comedy club is entirely front row. Not a nosebleed in sight! After all\, BYOB is just a drink special you never get tired of.
