SUMMARY:St. Patrick's Day at Annie Bailey's Irish Public House
DESCRIPTION:St. Patrick’s Day at Annie Bailey’s isn’t just a day—it’s a five-day celebration running March 13th through March 17th. As one of the only true Irish pubs in town\, this is what we do best. We’ll be pouring all your Irish favorites—Guinness\, Harp Lager\, Smithwick’s\, and Magners—alongside a special food menu packed with hearty Irish staples. \n\n\n\nExpect late-night entertainment all weekend long\, plus a special appearance by Irish dancers bringing authentic energy and tradition to the pub. On St. Patrick’s Day itself\, we’re opening early so you can celebrate from the first pint to the last call. Gather your crew\, wear your green\, and stop in to experience St. Patrick’s the way it’s meant to be—loud\, lively\, and unmistakably Irish. \n\n\n\nSláinte! 🍻
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/st-patricks-day-at-annie-baileys-irish-public-house-3/
LOCATION:Annie Bailey’s Irish Pub & Restaurant\, 28-30 East King Street\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
CATEGORIES:Free Events and Activites,Holiday,Music and Dance,Special Events
GEO:40.037678;-76.304243
