SUMMARY:Play It Forward: A Benefit Show for Lancaster Neighbor Fund
DESCRIPTION:Using improv to build a better world; one ticket at a time! Proceeds from ticket sales will go to the Lancaster Neighbor Fund. \n\n\n\nSince 2015\, Lancaster Improv Players has served our city through laughter; above all\, our mission is to make Lancaster a funnier place. Humor can be a balm in trying times\, and we wouldn’t be the first to say that laughter can be healing. Another important component of building a better world is making sure the programs helping out people in trying times are properly funded\, which is why we are going to PLAY IT FORWARD! \n\n\n\nAll proceeds from this event’s ticket sales will benefit the Lancaster Neighbor Fund. For those unfamiliar with LNF\, they provide direct financial support to immigrants who are vulnerable to deportation from Lancaster County. You can find out more about them and incredible work they do at their website; https://lancasterneighborfund.org/ \n\n\n\nEnjoy an hour of uproarious improv comedy from a curated collection of local talent\, AND build a better world through community care. It’s time to Play It Forward! \n\n\n\nFEATURING: GLORZEBUB and HIPPIE & FRENCHIE! \n\n\n\nBYOB$15 at the door \n\n\n\n(Our tickets are on a sliding scale; you are free to pay at a higher price point to boost the benefit!) \n\n\n\nDue to the size of our theater\, there is a quick turnover time between our scheduled shows. If you purchase tickets to both events on Saturday evening\, you will be asked to wait outside during the break so that the next team can warm up before the audience returns.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/play-it-forward-a-benefit-show-for-lancaster-neighbor-fund/
LOCATION:Lancaster Improv Players\, 16 S Prince St\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Theatre
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/play-it-forward.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Lancaster Improv Players":MAILTO:kate@lancasterimprovplayers.org
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR